        "title": "Our AI Platform Scores, Segments, and Converts",
        "keyMessage": "A three-layer AI system replaces manual effort with real-time personalized outreach",
        "layout": "bullets",
        "bullets": [
          "Layer 1 — Predictive Scoring: ML model trained on 5M customer events",
          "Layer 2 — Dynamic Segmentation: real-time cluster updates every 6 hours",
          "Layer 3 — Personalized Outreach: LLM-generated messaging per micro-segment",
          "Fully integrated with Salesforce, HubSpot, and Marketo",
          "Privacy-first design: zero PII leaves our data perimeter"
