  "chatMessages": [
    {
      "id": "msg-001",
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Create a 7-slide McKinsey-style deck for a board presentation on an AI-powered customer growth strategy. We want to show a 40% revenue uplift case.",
      "timestamp": 1741687200000
    },
    {
      "id": "msg-002",
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I've structured a 7-slide deck following the McKinsey action-title approach. Each slide leads with the main insight in the title so the story holds even if the audience only reads headlines.\n\n**Structure:**\n1. Title — headline outcome up front\n2. Agenda — orient the audience\n3. Problem — quantify what we're missing (the burning platform)\n4. Solution — three-layer AI platform overview\n5. Business case — financial projections at 3× ROI\n6. Roadmap — phased approach with go/no-go gates\n7. Ask — specific, time-bound investment request\n\nLet me know if you'd like to adjust the tone, add a competitive benchmarking slide, or swap any layout.",
      "timestamp": 1741687215000
    },
    {
      "id": "msg-003",
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The financial slide looks good. Can you make the ROI numbers more conservative? Change from 5× to 3× ROI.",
      "timestamp": 1741687380000
    },
    {
      "id": "msg-004",
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Updated Slide 5 to reflect conservative 3× ROI modelling. Changed:\n- ROI: 5× → **3×**\n- Payback period: 6 months → **8 months**\n- Net new ARR: $24M → **$18M** by end of Year 2\n\nThe upside case (5×) can live in an appendix slide if the board wants to see it.",
      "timestamp": 1741687395000
    }
  ],
